Package com.google.zxing.client.android.result

Class Summary
AddressBookResultHandler Handles address book entries.
CalendarResultHandler Handles calendar entries encoded in QR Codes.
EmailAddressResultHandler Handles email addresses.
GeoResultHandler Handles geographic coordinates (typically encoded as geo: URLs).
ISBNResultHandler Handles books encoded by their ISBN values.
ProductResultHandler Handles generic products which are not books.
ResultButtonListener Handles the result of barcode decoding in the context of the Android platform, by dispatching the proper intents to open other activities like GMail, Maps, etc.
ResultHandler A base class for the Android-specific barcode handlers.
ResultHandlerFactory Manufactures Android-specific handlers based on the barcode content's type.
SMSResultHandler Handles SMS addresses, offering a choice of composing a new SMS or MMS message.
TelResultHandler Offers relevant actions for telephone numbers.
TextResultHandler This class handles TextParsedResult as well as unknown formats.
URIResultHandler Offers appropriate actions for URLS.
WifiResultHandler Handles address book entries.
